Package: LinkedMatrix
Version: 1.2.0
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Title: Column-Linked and Row-Linked Matrices
Description: Matrices implemented as ordered collections of matrix-like nodes,
    linked by columns or rows. Particularly useful for memory-mapped matrices.
